==Getting around==
{{Main|/Transportation}}

[[Xeric's talisman]] and [[Kharedst's memoirs]] are the two most effective ways to get around Kourend and Kebos, but there are a variety of other useful methods, including the [[Lovakengj Minecart Network|minecart network]] and Magic spells. See the [[/Transportation|transportation guide]] for a full list, and maps.

==Favour==
{{main|Architectural Alliance#Gaining favour}}

Gaining favour from the different cities of Great Kourend is essential for progressing in Twisted League, since nearly all of the quests, and some of the best methods for training [[/Cooking|Cooking]], [[/Thieving|Thieving]], [[/Runecraft|Runecraft]] and [[/Mining|Mining]], are locked behind favour requirements. See [[Architectural Alliance#Gaining favour|the guide]] for strategies on quickly gaining favour.

